text: Henrique Honorato (born ) is a Brazilian indoor volleyball player. He is a current member of the Brazil men's national volleyball team. ==Career== He participated at the 2017 FIVB Volleyball Men's U21 World Championship and 2019 FIVB Volleyball Men's Nations League. ==Sporting achievements== ===National team=== * 2018 16px Pan-American Cup * 2019 16px Pan American Games ===Individuals=== * 2017 U21 Pan-American Cup – Best Outside Spiker ==References== ==External links== * FIVB Biography Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Brazilian men's volleyball players Category:People from Campina Grande Category:Pan American Games medalists in volleyball Category:Pan American Games bronze medalists for Brazil Category:Volleyball players at the 2019 Pan American Games
